<?xml version="1.0"?><h:html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:ev="http://www.w3.org/2001/xml-events" xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa" xmlns:odk="http://www.opendatakit.org/xforms" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"><h:head><h:title>OSCE_Spica bandage for thumb</h:title><model odk:xforms-version="1.0.0"><instance><data id="osce1_form" version="1.1"><intro><reserved_name_for_field_list_labels_3/><step1/><step2/><step3/><step4/></intro><meta><instanceID/></meta></data></instance><bind nodeset="/data/intro/reserved_name_for_field_list_labels_3" type="string"/><bind nodeset="/data/intro/step1" required="true()" type="string"/><bind nodeset="/data/intro/step2" required="true()" type="string"/><bind nodeset="/data/intro/step3" required="true()" type="string"/><bind nodeset="/data/intro/step4" required="true()" type="string"/><bind jr:preload="uid" nodeset="/data/meta/instanceID" readonly="true()" type="string"/></model></h:head><h:body class="pages"><group appearance="field-list" ref="/data/intro"><select1 appearance="label" ref="/data/intro/reserved_name_for_field_list_labels_3"><label> </label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step1"><label>Lay the free end of bandage across front of the wrist , leaving 4 inches free in order finally to tie the ends . carry the head of bandage across the back of thumb between thumb and forefinger . then take a wide spiral turn round the thumb within ½ inch of root of nail</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step2"><label>Take a turn round the thumb horizontally so that the lower border of bandage is ½ inch above root of nail</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step3"><label>Carry bandage down over the back of hand , round the wrist and repeat the figure of eight turns round thumb and wrist , until base of thumb is completely covered</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step4"><label>Finish off the bandage by one horizontal turn around the wrist , and tie off</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1></group></h:body></h:html>